{
  "texts": [
    "ConclusionAn overview of deep learning techniques used in watermarking and applied in images and video is presented in this survey paper.",
    "Firstly, watermarking terminology was presented, and traditional image and video watermarking techniques were classified based on their embedding domain.",
    "Then, deep learning-based image watermarking was classified and compared based on their network architecture.",
    "The survey also compared the four existing deep learning-based video watermarking proposed recently.",
    "Finally, this paper provided possible suggestions for future research in the field of video watermarking based on deep learning."
  ]
}